-program makes use of ncurses to create new windows
-monopoly.c is an old implementation that uses the regular linux terminal, use new_mon-
opoly.c. 
-Be sure to compile using the -lncurses flag, 'gcc new_monopoly.c -lncurses' to be prec-
ise.
-to learn more about ncurses, visit 'https://tldp.org/HOWTO/NCURSES-Programming-HOWTO/misc.html'

